  "title": "Core Concepts of Foundations of Introduction to Burmese Cuisine",
  "lessonText": "Explore the essential elements that define Burmese cuisine.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Emphasis on fresh ingredients.\n- Use of diverse spices and flavors.\n- Importance of balance between sweet, sour, salty, and bitter.\n- Influence from neighboring countries like India, China, and Thailand.\n- Traditional cooking methods such as steaming and frying."
